  <brief_title>The Role of EGFR Mutations in Pancreatic Cancer Patients Receiving Gemcitabine With or Without Erlotinib</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Role of Epidermal Growth Factor Receptor (EGFR) Mutations in Pancreatic Cancer Patients Receiving Gemcitabine With or Without Erlotinib</official_title>
  <sponsors>
