  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the influence of epidermal growth factor receptor
      mutations on the efficacy of erlotinib and gemcitabine in metastatic pancreatic cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The influence of EGFR mutations on the efficacy of treatment with and without erlotinib in
      metastatic pancreatic cancer is to be determined.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
